<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">* شُرُوطُ الصَّلَاةِ تِسْعَةٌ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الإِسْلَامُ، وَالعَقْلُ، وَالتَّمْيِيزُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَرَفْعُ الحَدَثِ، وَإِزَالَةُ النَّجَاسَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَسَتْرُ العَوْرَةِ، وَدُخُولُ الوَقْتِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَاسْتِقْبَالُ القِبْلَةِ، وَالنِّيَّةُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>